The paper discusses techniques and applications for crawling, ingesting, and analyzing Blockchain data, which involves aspects of cryptography, databases, distributed computing, information retrieval, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DB (Databases), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
